---
// src/components/Services.astro
---
<section id="services" class="main special">
	<header class="major">
		<h2>Our Services</h2>
	</header>
	<ul class="features">
		<li>
			<span class="icon solid major style3 fa-plane"></span>
			<h3>Air Ticketing</h3>
			<p>Full booking service for local and international flights, optimized to give your business the best rates.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span class="icon solid major style2 fa-hotel"></span>
			<h3>Hotel & Accommodation</h3>
			<p>Finding the best hotel accommodation options matched perfectly to your company budget and preferences.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span class="icon solid major style1 fa-car"></span>
			<h3>Car Hire & Transfers</h3>
			<p>Reliable airport pickups, private drivers, and group transport to keep your team moving safely.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span class="icon solid major style3 fa-calendar"></span>
			<h3>Event Management</h3>
			<p>Complete planning for business meetings, corporate conferences, and executive gatherings.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span class="icon solid major style2 fa-file"></span>
			<h3>Visas</h3>
			<p>Fast and accurate handling of visa applications.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span class="icon solid major style1 fa-user"></span>
			<h3>Dedicated Travel Consultants</h3>
			<p>Direct access to your own personal travel experts—no frustrating call centers or automated bots, just immediate human help when you need it.</p>
		</li>
	</ul>
</section>